Your listing immediately draw my attention. I am already looking for a place to live in Utrecht for nearly a year. Next year I am starting my second year at the university of Utrecht. I am 19 years old and a clean and tidy person. I love programming and other computer related items but also love watching a movie or having a drink with friends. I like to travel as well, I just came back from a trip through Europe to meet new people. People describe me as respectful, social, funny but also serious. I have had a year to have a small look into the life in Utrecht but now I really start to feel that I am not getting the whole experience which I really really would like to get. I am looking forward hearing from you.

With kind regards,
